Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.14,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:36.97,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:52.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:04.73,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:14.94,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.94,0:01:22.21,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.21,0:01:27.02,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:33.96,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko, it's Nanako on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.43,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell her I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.59,0:02:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only eight-thirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell her I'm not back home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened with you two? A quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't talk to her now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't bother waiting for Nanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.04,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to go home with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As a member of the Sorority, she has a lot of socializing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.05,0:02:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind that she is no longer an ordinary student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.91,0:03:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So how is Tomoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not back yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With regard to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...Henmi-san, the one who sent you the package...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your relationship with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! There's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just a teacher at our cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just a present he sent me for passing my entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's nice. Did you thank him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.55,0:03:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... but I wouldn't tell Dad about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want him worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's best...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course Misonoo-san's womanhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...should be especially good as far as cooking and selling is concerned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Her womanhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Her mother used to work at an establishment near Jyoto University...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,as a Cocktail Waitress!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at me that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, dear brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The more I try to believe Mom and Dad, the more doubts I seem to have...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm not brave enough to ask them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he really have another child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And another wife, the child's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.60,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,5. Thorns of Doubt and Suspicion
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I've got to get on the train, or I'm gonna be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What! She left half an hour earlier than usual?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko is avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps because I was chosen as a Sorority member?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:36.07,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,He was still silent, and seemed to be lost in thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:42.24,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,When I rose to leave, he did not invite me to stay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tomoko will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been together since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been friends a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that for sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.57,0:06:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So! What is your Cooking Club specialty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.91,0:06:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I picked cookies and baking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I think I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.45,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway! The story you just told me was... the funniest yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko, I need to talk to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.54,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't now. I have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't take long!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, there's someone waiting who is more your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness, Arikura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to prepare for the Sorority initiation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be the first ones there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Big Sisters frown on being late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sorority is our highest priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me so angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still taking these!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When will it sink in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When indeed, "Doctor" Orihara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have one left, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The light in your eyes makes me happy to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We are going to the Sorority House, Misonoo-san, Shinobu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be very helpful to us if you came too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Saint-Juste-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...she acts like a docile sheep whenever Miya-sama is nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.45,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to wear that bracelet forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Those flowers go there... and that table goes at the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And this white vase... to show off the flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, like that, close to the tapestry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Asaka-san... over here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.47,0:10:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you hold that corner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.10,0:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san... that should go on the table, on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.41,0:11:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood! Bloodstains!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please bandage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Komabayashi-san, take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let go of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly didn't imagine that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain that Miya-sama did that deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she acts just like a man would
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you insist on torturing yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.14,0:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, the new members will sign in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and will receive some flowers and a greeting from Fukiko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.63,0:13:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu Mariko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As an honorable Sorority member will you obey the rules of the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and dedicate yourself to develop the spirit of the Sorority with love and pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your smile is as refreshing as an azalea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, never lose that lovely smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo Nanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As an honorable Sorority member will you obey the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The love that you receive
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,comes from the love you create within the kindness of your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.31,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I didn't call first...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, geez, what's with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako, you've been in such a weird mood all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,When you bandaged Sainte-Juste, all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you realize that Miya-sama was glaring at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave me a cold sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Don't defy Miya-sama! You can't go against her will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:16:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be voted out of the Sorority at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, her father is on the Board of Directors at our school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you even listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My dear Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not tell anyone what Miya-sama did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor about Saint-Juste's attitude toward Miya-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...these glimpses of their true feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all beyond my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it frightens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never been able to forgive us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I blamed you for taking my father away from us,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I resented my father for loving you more than my mother and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept sending money until I was an adult... even after Mother died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, every month you couldn't have done it on a professor's salary alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As I grew older...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...I began to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To forgive or not to forgive... to blame or not to blame...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally the issue somehow didn't seem important anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Takehiko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.68,0:17:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako is charming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to feel... like she really is my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I first found out, I was shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Be my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo? Daughter of Professor Misonoo of Jyoto University?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.11,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Accepting her request meant that eventually you would find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, if I could do something for her as a brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one request... please...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't told Nanako that her father has another child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.22,0:19:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If we tell her, she'd be hurt unnecessarily, and blame us, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't have to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just be one among many... a friend she confided in, during her adolescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako! You'll hurt yourself! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...the hand which touched my hair, that often tossed the ball to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,handing me "Tom Sawyer", cleaning out his pipe... only 6 months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... I've lost you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I should never have come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That was you on the phone just now, I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get even for today, for hurting me so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The love that you receive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,comes from the love you create within the kindness of your own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.88,0:22:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, love creates hate and doubt and anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be afraid of people hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.69,0:22:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you do get hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.96,0:22:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...then hurt the person who hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.46,0:23:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako... are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing... I'm ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't go back to sleep, come to my study,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be up for awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.69,0:23:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It rained until just before dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.79,0:24:13.99,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:19.47,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.93,0:24:25.07,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.07,0:24:30.54,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.28,0:24:36.82,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.82,0:24:42.29,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.29,0:24:45.03,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.03,0:24:47.83,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.83,0:24:50.23,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.23,0:24:55.50,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.31,0:25:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako's gym clothes, missing from her locker, are finally found. They are shredded.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.65,0:25:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The petition to oust her from the Sorority continues to circulate.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.57,0:25:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako finally decides to leave the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.79,0:25:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Lost and Alone
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.99,0:25:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
